<section class="method-section" id="method">
	<div class="method-inner">
		<div class="method-grid">
			<p class="method-statement">
				<strong>Most meditation systems are trying to fix you.</strong> They
				suggest that you are fundamentally broken.
			</p>

			<div class="method-copy">
				<p>
					There is nothing fundamentally wrong with you.<br />
					You can remain connected and present in any circumstance, however
					frightening or exciting it may seem. You will develop the capacity to
					hold the intensity, the joy, and the ordinary textures of existence with
					spacious clarity.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
